			<td class="xar-norm author">
				<div><a href="http://www.ldonline.org/roles/28438">RickRun</a></div>
				<div class="xar-sub">
										Joined: Aug 28, 2009<br/>Posts: 5										<br /><a href="http://www.ldonline.org/xarbb?by=28438&amp;func=searchtopics">Other Topics</a>
